<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 12:11:05 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>近东救济工程处是什么？它服务的巴勒斯坦难民是谁？为什么各国冻结资金？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/what-is-unrwa-and-why-are-countries-freezing-their-funding/0000018d-550e-d0fc-a9bd-5f5f45020000</link><description>该联合国机构提供教育、卫生和社会服务，并在战争时期提供救生援助和庇护所，目前是加沙最大的雇主之一。但有关哈马斯参与的指控可能会危及其行动</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 11:32:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/what-is-unrwa-and-why-are-countries-freezing-their-funding/0000018d-550e-d0fc-a9bd-5f5f45020000</guid></item><item><title>阿拉伯裔以色列校长在学校外遭枪击，受轻伤；警方逮捕四名嫌疑人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/arab-israeli-principal-shot-wounded-outside-his-school-police-arrest-four-suspects/0000018d-59a8-d0fc-a9bd-5ffdcef60000</link><description>当局认为这起枪击事件与受害者大家庭之间的一场争斗有关。校长的兄弟 Hussam 去年 7 月被谋杀，享年 45 岁</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 11:02:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/arab-israeli-principal-shot-wounded-outside-his-school-police-arrest-four-suspects/0000018d-59a8-d0fc-a9bd-5ffdcef60000</guid></item><item><title>在美国压力下，巴勒斯坦总理宣布全面振兴巴勒斯坦权力机构</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/following-u-s-pressure-palestinian-pm-declares-broad-revitalization-of-pa/0000018d-5987-d0fc-a9bd-5fdf5c750000</link><description>穆罕默德·什塔耶表示，新计划将分阶段实施，包括安全、经济和医疗保健方面的重大变化，但巴勒斯坦高级官员仍怀疑此举能否改善与以色列的关系</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 10:41:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/following-u-s-pressure-palestinian-pm-declares-broad-revitalization-of-pa/0000018d-5987-d0fc-a9bd-5fdf5c750000</guid></item><item><title>以色列支持拒绝释放亿万富翁罗曼·阿布拉莫维奇的捐赠资金</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/israel-backs-refusal-to-release-billionaire-roman-abramovichs-funds-for-a-donation/0000018d-5601-d997-adff-df7be6320000</link><description>由于俄罗斯制裁，一家以色列银行拒绝从俄罗斯-以色列寡头的账户中转出220万美元，用于向以色列扎卡搜救组织捐款。总检察长表示她正在保护以色列银行免受风险</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 09:35:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/israel-backs-refusal-to-release-billionaire-roman-abramovichs-funds-for-a-donation/0000018d-5601-d997-adff-df7be6320000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队伪装成医生突袭约旦河西岸医院，打死三名哈马斯恐怖分子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-forces-raid-west-bank-hospital-dressed-as-doctors-kill-three-hamas-terrorists/0000018d-5968-d997-adff-dd7aba630000</link><description>一支以色列卧底部队袭击了杰宁的伊本西纳医院，杀死了三名哈马斯附属人员。以色列安全部队表示，三人计划在不久的将来发动袭击</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 09:34:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-forces-raid-west-bank-hospital-dressed-as-doctors-kill-three-hamas-terrorists/0000018d-5968-d997-adff-dd7aba630000</guid></item><item><title>尽管美国和卡塔尔持乐观态度，但以色列与哈马斯的协议仍然难以实现</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/despite-american-and-qatari-optimism-israel-hamas-deal-remains-elusive/0000018d-56f0-d997-adff-dffa95590000</link><description>美国需要一项成就 — — 比如释放以色列人质 — — 但它已经对内塔尼亚胡的政策失去了耐心 ■ 伊朗尚未为其地区骚乱付出代价，华盛顿正在努力避免局势进一步升级 ■ 真主党正在准备与以色列国防军迫在眉睫的广泛冲突</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 04:00:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/despite-american-and-qatari-optimism-israel-hamas-deal-remains-elusive/0000018d-56f0-d997-adff-dffa95590000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯主席伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚表示，该组织已收到巴黎停火提案，将进行研究</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article-live/blinken-urges-unrwa-to-act-on-highly-credible-allegations-against-staffers-in-gaza/0000018d-5876-d997-adff-dd7e7b5f0000</link><description>布林肯将于周六访问以色列 ■ 布林肯敦促近东救济工程处对针对加沙工作人员的“高度可信”指控采取行动 ■ 英国外交部表示，英国考虑承认巴勒斯坦国 ■ 三名被通缉的哈马斯成员在以色列国防军袭击杰宁医院时被杀 ■ 卡塔尔总理称在实现这一目标方面取得了进展人质交易 ■ 一名士兵在海法袭击中受重伤 ■ 两名士兵在以色列北部被真主党火箭弹轻伤</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 03:49:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article-live/blinken-urges-unrwa-to-act-on-highly-credible-allegations-against-staffers-in-gaza/0000018d-5876-d997-adff-dd7e7b5f0000</guid></item><item><title>现在在加沙隧道内作战，以色列国防军知道杀死哈马斯领导人不会结束其统治</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/now-fighting-inside-gaza-tunnels-idf-knows-that-killing-hamas-leaders-wont-end-its-rule/0000018d-572b-d0fc-a9bd-5f7fa3850000</link><description>以色列高级军官相信，哈马斯地道内的战斗将提供有关该组织领导人及其仍扣押的以色列人质的宝贵情报</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 01:15:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/now-fighting-inside-gaza-tunnels-idf-knows-that-killing-hamas-leaders-wont-end-its-rule/0000018d-572b-d0fc-a9bd-5f7fa3850000</guid></item><item><title>总理办公室同意修复内塔尼亚胡私人住宅泳池后，以色列官员辞职</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-official-to-quit-after-pms-bureau-okays-repairs-to-pool-at-netanyahus-home/0000018d-570b-d997-adff-df7becd90000</link><description>首席会计师与总理办公室其他官员发生冲突，最近一次是因为内塔尼亚胡位于凯撒利亚的庞大住宅的游泳池和住宅区的维修问题</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 00:08:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-official-to-quit-after-pms-bureau-okays-repairs-to-pool-at-netanyahus-home/0000018d-570b-d997-adff-df7becd90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战时内阁讨论哈马斯人质交易；消息人士称，大多数问题都已达成共识</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/israeli-war-cabinet-discusses-hostage-deal-sources-uderstandings-emerge-on-most-issues/0000018d-56be-d0fc-a9bd-5eff2c950000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡办公室否认谈判取得进展的报道，但接受国土报采访的消息人士表示，核心问题是停火问题。周一早些时候，作为谈判的一部分，以色列代表团访问了埃及</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 21:00:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/israeli-war-cabinet-discusses-hostage-deal-sources-uderstandings-emerge-on-most-issues/0000018d-56be-d0fc-a9bd-5eff2c950000</guid></item><item><title>“你在他们的鲜血上跳舞”：以色列人质家庭对重新安置会议感到愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/youre-dancing-on-their-blood-hostage-families-outraged-over-resettlement-conference/0000018d-5679-d0fc-a9bd-5e7d6c8b0000</link><description>以色列人质家属在议会发言，指责出席会议的内塔尼亚胡政府十一位部长“放弃他们”，而人质协议仍未达成</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 19:52:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/youre-dancing-on-their-blood-hostage-families-outraged-over-resettlement-conference/0000018d-5679-d0fc-a9bd-5e7d6c8b0000</guid></item><item><title>美国称以色列加沙重新安置的呼吁“鲁莽”，本格维尔加倍努力驱逐“试点”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/u-s-says-calls-for-gaza-settlement-reckless-as-ben-gvir-doubles-down-on-expulsion-pilot/0000018d-560a-d0fc-a9bd-5e5f15200000</link><description>在呼吁犹太人重新安置加沙的会议一天后，本-格维尔强调，在中间派战时内阁部长批评这次会议后，巴勒斯坦人的自愿移民至关重要。美国、法国和德国也谴责这些呼吁“不负责任”</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 19:32:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/u-s-says-calls-for-gaza-settlement-reckless-as-ben-gvir-doubles-down-on-expulsion-pilot/0000018d-560a-d0fc-a9bd-5e5f15200000</guid></item><item><title>以色列情报报告指责近东救济工程处 190 名工作人员是“顽固”武装分子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/israel-accuses-190-unrwa-staff-of-being-hardened-militants-intel-memo-alleges/0000018d-5637-d0fc-a9bd-5e7fcbd50000</link><description>以色列公布的一份长达六页的档案称，近东救济工程处 13,000 名员工中，有 10% 与哈马斯有一般联系，其中有 190 名“杀手” ■ 10 个国家已停止向该机构提供资金</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 18:23:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/israel-accuses-190-unrwa-staff-of-being-hardened-militants-intel-memo-alleges/0000018d-5637-d0fc-a9bd-5e7fcbd50000</guid></item><item><title>具有新纳粹根源的瑞典极右政党高层成员在以色列议会会见以色列部长</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/top-members-of-far-right-swedish-party-with-neo-nazi-roots-meet-israeli-minister/0000018d-564e-d0fc-a9bd-5e5f9ff00000</link><description>由于瑞典民主党成员表达了反犹太主义和仇视伊斯兰教的情绪，以色列迄今为止一直没有与瑞典民主党接触。党员告诉《国土报》，他们在访问期间会见了几位部长，但拒绝透露他们的姓名</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 18:08:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/top-members-of-far-right-swedish-party-with-neo-nazi-roots-meet-israeli-minister/0000018d-564e-d0fc-a9bd-5e5f9ff00000</guid></item><item><title>以上帝之名进行种族清洗：唯一对加沙“后天”有计划的以色列人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/ethnic-cleansing-in-gods-name-the-only-israelis-with-a-plan-for-the-day-after-in-gaza/0000018d-55e0-d997-adff-ddfa9b490000</link><description>周日，约 5,000 名定居者聚集在耶路撒冷，庆祝他们为重新定居加沙地带所做的努力，并使弥赛亚的到来更近了一步。他们在以色列仍然是少数派，这一事实并没有引起他们的关注</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 17:13:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/ethnic-cleansing-in-gods-name-the-only-israelis-with-a-plan-for-the-day-after-in-gaza/0000018d-55e0-d997-adff-ddfa9b490000</guid></item><item><title>周一，在约旦河西岸发生的四起事件中，五名巴勒斯坦人被以色列军队开火打死</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/five-palestinians-killed-by-israeli-army-fire-in-four-separate-west-bank-incidents/0000018d-5599-d0fc-a9bd-5fddaadd0000</link><description>以色列军队称，一名年轻人在亚蒙村向以色列国防军士兵开枪后被杀；另外两名巴勒斯坦人在杜拉被杀，另一名青年在以色列特科亚定居点附近被杀，另一名青年在拉马拉附近被杀</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 16:27:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/five-palestinians-killed-by-israeli-army-fire-in-four-separate-west-bank-incidents/0000018d-5599-d0fc-a9bd-5fddaadd0000</guid></item><item><title>在内塔尼亚胡的鼓励下，犹太人至上和反民主的狂热狂欢</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/an-orgy-of-jewish-supremacy-and-antidemocratic-euphoria-encouraged-by-netanyahu/0000018d-556b-d0fc-a9bd-5f7f8b540000</link><description>美国总统乔·拜登下次与本杰明·内塔尼亚胡谈论中东重组问题时应该记住周日极右翼会议上呼吁重新安置加沙的场景</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 16:26:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/an-orgy-of-jewish-supremacy-and-antidemocratic-euphoria-encouraged-by-netanyahu/0000018d-556b-d0fc-a9bd-5f7f8b540000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡受贿案辩护律师要求辞职</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-defense-attorney-in-bribery-case-asks-to-step-down/0000018d-54e1-d1b6-aded-5fe929d20000</link><description>总理表示，提出这一要求的原因是他的律师的家人生病了。在另外两起刑事案件中代表内塔尼亚胡的律师阿米特·哈达德表示，他也愿意在贿赂案中代表他</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 15:52:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-defense-attorney-in-bribery-case-asks-to-step-down/0000018d-54e1-d1b6-aded-5fe929d20000</guid></item><item><title>据《华尔街日报》报道，近东救济工程处在加沙的大约 10% 员工与哈马斯、伊斯兰圣战组织有联系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/wsj-about-10-percent-of-unrwa-employees-in-gaza-have-ties-to-hamas-islamic-jihad/0000018d-5565-d8cc-a1fd-576f89eb0000</link><description>以色列官员向《华尔街日报》报道称，参与加沙哈马斯活动的联合国巴勒斯坦难民机构（近东救济工程处）雇员数量“不仅仅是几个害群之马”。随着指控的继续调查，九个国家已暂时停止向该组织提供资金</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 15:36:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/wsj-about-10-percent-of-unrwa-employees-in-gaza-have-ties-to-hamas-islamic-jihad/0000018d-5565-d8cc-a1fd-576f89eb0000</guid></item><item><title>“以色列人民将解决加沙问题”：内塔尼亚胡的部长们在极右翼会议上支持驱逐巴勒斯坦人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-people-of-israel-will-settle-gaza-netanyahu-ministers-urge-palestinians-expulsion/0000018d-5495-d1b6-aded-5fdd570c0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡的通讯部长在台上宣称，“自愿”[移民]有时是你强加的情况，直到他们同意为止。”他揭露了“以色列胜利会议”的真实信息：转移或驱逐，来自加沙的巴勒斯坦人</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 15:32:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-people-of-israel-will-settle-gaza-netanyahu-ministers-urge-palestinians-expulsion/0000018d-5495-d1b6-aded-5fdd570c0000</guid></item></channel></rss>